edback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mif1665703178050.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mif1665703178050.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mif1665703178050.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mif1665703178050\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Parses a line from a single-line or multi-line response from an SMTP server into the reply code and the associated message.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mif1665703178050__topic_d132584e1_d132585e1_d132586e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mif1665703178050__p_d132587e1_d132588e1_d132589e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int ParseReply(unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Reply</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, int</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ReplyLen</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, int *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Code</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, int *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Offset</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, int *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Last</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, unsigned char **</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mif1665703178050__section_h34_gq1_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186605e96\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\"> Name </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> Direction </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Reply</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Reply </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> int * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ReplyLen</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Length of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Reply</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> int * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Code</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Reply code </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> int * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Offset</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Offset from start of reply to the textual message\n              </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> int * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Last</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\"> Flag set to indicate last or only line </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char ** </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15803e1_d15804e1_d15805e1__entry__4\">Pointer to next line. The caller should not change\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var> between calls. When starting with a\n                reply, <code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var> must be 0. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mif1665703178050__section_w3808ab1b5b5_w3809ab1b5_w3810ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186605e260\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__1\"> &gt;= 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__2\"> Length of the message text without the CRLF\n                termination. There are no more lines in the reply when <var class=\"keyword varname\">Last</var> is\n                non-zero. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__1\"> -1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__2\">Internal call error; syntax or call is not understood. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__1\"> -2 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__2\">Line does not start with a digit. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__1\"> -3 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mif1665703178050__table_d15806e1_d15807e1_d15808e1__entry__2\">Line does not end with CRLF. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mif1665703178050__section_w3811ab1b5b7_w3812ab1b5_w3813ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186605e330\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mif1665703178050__p_d132599e1_d132600e1_d132601e1\">This function parses a line from a single-line or\n        multi-line response from an SMTP server into the reply code and the associated message. The\n        function can be used to walk through the lines of a multi-line response. The line format\n        is:</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessNum</var>{sp | <code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessText</var> CRLF</p>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mif1665703178050__parml_e4k_5q1_fwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">MessNum</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">3-digit number</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">sp (space)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Iindicates that it is a single line reply or the last line of reply </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">- (hyphen)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Indicates that it is a multi-line response </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">MessText</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Associated message text</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">CRLF</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Carriage return and line feed characters </dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mif1665703178050__p_d132605e1_d132606e1_d132607e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mif1665703178050_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mif1665703178050__codeblock_mfl_4q1_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">123-First line\n123-Second line\n123-234 Text beginning with numbers\n123 Last line\n\nlen = ParseReply(sec-&gt;InBuf, sec-&gt;InDataLen, &amp;code, &amp;offset, &amp;last, &amp;next);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529931\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529931\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ParseReply Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Parses a line from a single-line or multi-line response from an SMTP server into the reply code and the associated message. int ParseReply(unsigned char * Reply , int ReplyLen , int * Code , int * Offset , int * Last , unsigned char ** Next ) Parameters Type Name Direction Description unsigned char * Reply IN Reply int * ReplyLen IN Length of Reply int * Code OUT Reply code int * Offset OUT Offset from start of reply to the textual message int * Last OUT Flag set to indicate last or only line unsigned char ** Next OUT Pointer to next line. The caller should not change * Next between calls. When starting with a reply, * Next must be 0. Return Values Value Description >= 0 Length of the message text without the CRLF termination. There are no more lines in the reply when Last is non-zero. -1 Internal call error; syntax or call is not understood. -2 Line does not start with a digit. -3 Line does not end with CRLF. Description This function parses a line from a single-line or multi-line response from an SMTP server into the reply code and the associated message. The function can be used to walk through the lines of a multi-line response. The line format is: MessNum {sp | - } MessText CRLF MessNum 3-digit number sp (space) Iindicates that it is a single line reply or the last line of reply - (hyphen) Indicates that it is a multi-line response MessText Associated message text CRLF Carriage return and line feed characters For example: Explain this code 123-First line 123-Second line 123-234 Text beginning with numbers 123 Last line len = ParseReply(sec->InBuf, sec->InDataLen, &code, &offset, &last, &next); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}